definitions.definition: A soft tap or blow ; a blow or peck from a bird's beak; an aimed blow.
( African-American Vernacular ) A soft, playful box given in greeting or approval.
A small amount, a blob of some soft or wet substance.

subdefinitions.definition: ( slang ) A small amount of hash oil .

definitions.definition: ( chiefly in the plural , dated , British ) Fingerprint .
( dance ) A hip hop dance move in which the dancer simultaneously drops the head while raising an arm, briefly resting their face in the elbow, as if sneezing into their elbow.

main_definition: A soft tap or blow ; a blow or peck from a bird's beak; an aimed blow.

definitions.definition: One who is skilful or proficient ; an expert; an adept .

main_definition: One who is skilful or proficient ; an expert; an adept .

definitions.definition: A small flatfish of the family Pleuronectidae , especially Limanda limanda ; a flounder.
A sand dab , a small flatfish of genus Citharichthys .
